embeddedItem.name: Lil' Twisty Bubble Gum
embeddedItem.desc: A tasty and cheap Punklorde snack. Can be used to Superimpose the Light Cone "Before the Tutorial Mission Starts."
embeddedItem.lore:
A candy favored by a certain Stellaron Hunter. It contains rocket tree gum, and the crispy sound of bubbles popping is absolutely irresistible.

"Pop!"
